values.description: The Wwise authoring application, a graphical user interface that centralizes all aspects of audio creation. The authoring application is required to edit Wwise projects and to generate SoundBanks.
The Wwise authoring application along with the debug DLLs and symbols for plug-in developers.
The C++ include files and several configurations of the compiled libraries and symbols. It includes SDK code samples and documentation. This is not required for Unity Development.
The Wwise User Guide PDF and the Wwise Help CHM.

The C++ source code of the Wwise SDK. A license for the Source Code is required per Deployment Platform, the license status can be viewed in the Customer Portal. Contact Audiokinetic sales for more information.
A LUA interpreter with Wwise SDK bindings.
The award-winning LIMBO game with complete Wwise project and companion documentation.
A full open-source game with C++ source code, Wwise project, and companion documentation.
A Wwise Project and companion documentation demonstrating Wwise features.

children.name: Auro Headphone
children.description: Auro-3D is the next generation three-dimensional audio standard. It provides the most immersive and natural realistic 3D sound experience.

children.name: iZotope suite
children.description: iZotope offers a suite of their most popular sound design plug-ins for use directly within Wwise. The suite of Trash tools and Hybrid Reverb can take your sound design projects to the next level.

children.name: McDSP ML1, McDSP Futzbox
children.description: McDSP brings a selection of their award-winning plug-ins directly to Wwise: FutzBox Lo-Fi Distortion and ML1 Mastering Limiter.

children.name: Wwise Reflect
children.description: Wwise Reflect is a geometry-informed plug-in that dynamically renders early reflections based on the proximity of the listener/emitter to reflective surfaces, such as walls, ceilings, and floors.

children.name: Wwise SoundSeed Air, Wwise SoundSeed Impact
children.description: Wwise SoundSeed is a family of specialized sound generators. Crafted with interactive audio in mind, these plug-ins help saving on CPU and memory while generating infinite variations.
children.displayName: Wwise SoundSeed Air, Wwise SoundSeed Impact 2021.1.0.7575

children.name: Wwise Motion
children.description: Wwise Motion plug-in adds the haptic feedback of a control interface.

children.name: Mastering Suite
children.description: The Mastering Suite is a cross-platform high quality mastering solution providing subtle to surgical manipulation to your mix. Support various rendering scenarios by controlling the dynamic range, equalization curve, limiting and gain of individual channels.
